1. Use Automator to create a new 'Quick Action' which is installed as a new 'Service' on the OS.
[Saved an installable service in ~/Dropbox/LatchDropbox/LaunchTerminal]

2. System Preferences -> Keyboard -> Shortcuts -> Find your service (e.g. Launch Terminal) -> Add a shortcut

-- Should be good to go after that.

